{"tid":2114064,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"北區中學校長會向北區區議會申請撥款舉辦「北區中學聯校普通話演講比賽」， 委員會根據表決通過。","createTime":"2020-07-18T13:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T06:35:59.000Z","uid":320487,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1e7fdd144b6c9a94f2e121d872042805d4c670","tid":2114064,"uid":320487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"【朗誦比賽語言由普通話轉至粵語】<br />\n.<br />\n北區中學校長會早前向北區區議會申請撥款，以舉辦「北區中學聯校普通話演講比賽」。<br />\n.<br />\n對於比賽語言採用普通話，委員就此提出質疑。委員認為粵語更能讓本土學生以母語發揮，亦能讓鼓勵跨境或新移民同學融入本土粵語文化，更加適合作為比賽語言。<br />\n.<br />\n我動議要求議員就該比賽語言表態，結果零票普通話，一票英文，一票客家話，其餘所有委員全投粵語。<br />\n.<br />\n委員會根據表決結果，向北區中學校長提出條件，要求將比賽語言由「普通話」改為「粵語」，意味著如果北區中學校長會堅持把比賽語言定為「普通話」，將不會獲得區議會批出任何撥款。<br />\n.<br />\n#北區中學校長會 #北區中學聯校演講比賽 #粵語 #普通話 #捍衛本土<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chiangmanching/photos/a.103274661023835/299626891388610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchiangmanching%2Fphotos%2Fa.103274661023835%2F299626891388610&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=59f8d3e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chiangmanching/photos/a.103274661023835/299626891388610</a>"},{"pid":"91a0c9aa8bef2f1a55cb5929b622e39ce86f91b4","tid":2114064,"uid":8596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:55:00.000Z","msg":"一票客家話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c56218feb2384a0221a5dc7c5fa0baf3c93954","tid":2114064,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:58:12.000Z","msg":"北區中學聯校潮語演講比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1b9709dde891d64196cb3f36f239eaaa1e6b086","tid":2114064,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T06:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpwtP7N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCpwtP7N.jpg&h=03e8a8f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AEQBY09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAEQBY09.jpg&h=f1e213ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gfN5Ga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gfN5Ga.jpg&h=1e131b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xS2T1eD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxS2T1eD.jpg&h=34afa5d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">呢12個界别要人吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勸合資格嘅朋友、家人、同事參選吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"}]}